{"tid":1528311,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[Be Water]浮生若水 - 林峯","createTime":"2019-09-01T13:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T14:14:28.000Z","uid":108757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ab6cb9fb9e19b1d20a256685f358b45c4e9e85","tid":1528311,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T13:35:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=00LAuGtBsiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D00LAuGtBsiU&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702D2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=ef6c6790\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=00LAuGtBsiU</a><br />\n即使身處<span style=\"color: red;\">逆流未畏懼</span> <br />\n我兩手一轉勢便浮浪午睡 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">任潮浪再巨 也終歸跌碎</span> <br />\n何妨學習<span style=\"color: red;\">輕舟懂得戲水</span> <br />\n假使所愛流離在對岸 <br />\n我的心肯輕放便難被碰撞 <br />\n為誰而震蕩 <span style=\"color: red;\">沒法守便放</span> <br />\n離離合合悲悲喜喜似水 <span style=\"color: red;\">別強擋</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">善</span>莫善於水 輕與重 也<span style=\"color: red;\">借勢推送</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">柔弱</span>莫弱於水 水轉動 卸去了心痛 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">容大</span>莫大於水 將壓力 化清風 <br />\n磨到 頑石也融 將恨意歸空 <br />\n<br />\n不爭先氣度才無處覓<br />\n永遠<span style=\"color: red;\">不執於友敵</span>才無敵<br />\n動搖沒法靜 要<span style=\"color: red;\">懂得用勁</span><br />\n浮沉順逆轉身不沾背影 像泡影<br />\n善莫善於水 輕與重 也借勢推送 <br />\n柔弱莫弱於水 水轉動 卸去了心痛 <br />\n容大莫大於水 將壓力 化清風 <br />\n磨到 頑石也融 將恨意歸空<br />\n<br />\n善莫善於水 水向下 <span style=\"color: red;\">退了也可進</span><br />\n柔弱莫弱於水 水舞動 <span style=\"color: red;\">哪裡要操控</span><br />\n容大莫大於水 山與岸 被簇擁<br />\n直到<span style=\"color: red;\">頑石失蹤</span> 只<span style=\"color: red;\">望見清空</span><br />\n<br />\n好深奧，有無人解釋下？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73631523d853cad2e613fb596140223bbf9b2670","tid":1528311,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"不要說推<br />\n要說中國違反 + 廢除《中英聯合聲明》"},{"pid":"bd73747128cd7eea958506f4b0a6b884d4a3b838","tid":1528311,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:14:28.000Z","msg":"不要說推<br />\n要說中國違反 + 廢除《中英聯合聲明》"}]}